OL,4,Cwho was riding his bike
OL,6,FA BMW driver who hit and killed a 12-
OL,7,Fyear-old boy in Birmingham has been
OL,8,Fjailed for for dangerous driving.
OL,10,FShazad Alam was driving a BMW M3 along
OL,11,FCoventry Road on Saturday 8 June when
OL,12,Fhe hit 12-year-old Azaan Khan, who was
OL,13,Fcrossing the road on his bicycle.
OL,15,FWest Midlands Police estimate Alam was
OL,16,Fdriving between 53 and 62 mph just
OL,17,Fbefore he hit Azaan, in a 40mph limit.
