OL,6,FThe 34-year-old had previously pleaded
OL,7,Fnot guilty, before admitting dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving at Birmingham Crown Court in
OL,9,FSeptember.
OL,11,FAzaan was cycling home after a trip to
OL,12,Fthe shops with his friend he was hit
OL,13,Fby Alam's car. He died at the scene.
OL,15,F"No parent should endure this kind of
OL,16,Fheartbreak and pain."
