OL,6,FHis family paid an emotional tribute
OL,7,Fto their son, saying: "It's been over
OL,8,Fa year since our boy was taken from
OL,9,Fus, yet we still can't accept the
OL,10,Freality that he's gone.
OL,12,F"Azaan was our light, our comfort when
OL,13,Flife becomes too heavy, our warmth
OL,14,Fwhen the world felt cold.
OL,16,F"He had a great sense of humour and a
OL,17,Fcharm like no other. His smile and
OL,18,Fcharisma would fill any room he was
OL,19,Fin. He left an imprint on anyone who
OL,20,Fwas luckily enough to meet him.
