OL,6,F"We can only hope that Azaan's name,
OL,7,Fhis story, will do something and will
OL,8,Fmake people realise that we cannot let
OL,9,Fthis be normal.
OL,11,F"No parent should endure this kind of
OL,12,Fheartbreak and pain."
