OL,3,CDriver jailed after killing, boy, 12,
OL,4,Cwho was riding his bike
OL,6,FDet Sgt Paul Hughes said: "This tragic
OL,7,Fincident shows the real consequences
OL,8,Fof getting behind the wheel of a car
OL,9,Fand driving in a clearly aggressive
OL,10,Fmanner.
OL,12,F"This type of driving is not
OL,13,Facceptable on any of our roads. I need
OL,14,Fall drivers to look at this and other
OL,15,Fcases and realise the consequences of
OL,16,Fthose split-second decisions they make.
OL,18,F"Our thoughts are with Azaan's loved
OL,19,Fones."
